Colliers and CBRE are pleased to offer for lease 181 Broadway, Ultimo.

Located centrally and prominently on the corner of Mountain and Broadway, this is one of Ultimo’s best positioned buildings for exposure, sitting within minutes’ walk to UTS, Central Park, Central station and the new tech precinct.

Exuding stunning heritage features, the tenancy includes large arched window, oversized 7m+ ceilings and beautiful timber floors throughout.

Key highlights:
- Size: 158sqm*-550sqm*
- Rich with heritage features, well suited to creative occupiers
- Well suited to many uses – office, fitness, food & beverage, showroom
- Well portioned and efficient floorplate
- Exclusive bathrooms and kitchen
-	Air-conditioning throughout
-	Large basement storage
-	Natural light from 2 sides
-	Prominent corner position and high exposure area
-	Economical parking options available closeby.
-	Easy walk to Central Station and numerous bus links at your doorstep.

This rare opportunity, offers its new occupier endless opportunities, please contact the listing agents for further information.

CBRE and Fringe Commercial are pleased to offer 55 Mountain Street, Ultimo to the market for lease.

A character building with high ceilings, exposed brick and original timber beams, the space is fully fitted out with a boardroom, meeting room, full kitchen and breakout area and open plan working area for 25+ workstations.

Located moments from Broadway Shopping Centre, major bus links on Broadway, as well as walking distance to Central Train Station.

Key Highlights:
• 283sqm
• Fully fitted out suite
• Character building with exposed brick interiors and original timber beams
• Ducted air-conditioning throughout (separately metered)
• Direct lift access, DDA compliant building
• Natural light from three sides
• High speed fibre-optic connection available
• End of Trip facilities on site
• Secure parking available on site
• Significant lobby upgrade underway
• Café located on the ground floor, and plenty of restaurants/cafes/bars in the immediate vicinity

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Bring your business moments from Central Station at 458 Wattle Street, Ultimo.  Fitted out with executive offices, end of trip facilities, a functional boardroom with direct balcony access and IT cabling, this turnkey solution is ready to occupy.

The suite benefits from an efficient layout, with an abundance of natural light from two sides.  Suited to a multitude of office users, the incoming tenant can either utilise the current furniture and fit out or make changes as they see fit.

• 217sqm*
• Very fair asking rental
• Fitted and furnished - Board room and 2 executive offices, workstations and storage
• Direct lift access to whole floor tenancy
• Cabled and ready to occupy, equipped with server room (and supplementary AC unit) if required
• 1 car space
• Shower, kitchenette as well as male & female toilets
• Tiled balcony with excellent aspect and soaked in sunlight
• High quality carpet
• Pigeonhole Café on ground level

For further information or to organise an inspection, please get in touch with the exclusive agents.
